Version: 3 (05.01.2013)

Make TXT file with ed2k link for each file.
FileName is "AnimeName - EpNo [Group][CRC32].ext".
Warning: Anime and group names comes "as is" (with spaces and symbols like ':?*/|\' etc).
Lines separated by 0Dh 0Ah symbols.
Generic, deleted, corrupted in any way files and files without CRC32 are not listed.
Files over multiple episodes are commented out by ";" char (I can't find any other way to get rid of them)

Purpose is for automated HDD audit.

Feel free to send PM about this report.
